---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="GP — Entry Requirements" description="RACGP AGPT general practice training entry requirements and application.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Entry Requirements</h1>
    <p>General Practice — RACGP AGPT</p>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>2027 Intake Applications</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Applications close 14 April 2026</div>
      <p>Apply via the AGPT program portal. ~90+ Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander doctors currently in training.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Eligibility Criteria</h2>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li>Medical degree from a recognised institution</li>
      <li>General registration with AHPRA <span class="tag">AU</span></li>
      <li>Eligibility to work in Australia</li>
      <li>Entry assessment requirements (details in AGPT application guide)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Recognition of Prior Learning</h2>
    <p>The AGPT program offers recognition of prior learning, which may reduce total training duration for eligible applicants with relevant prior experience.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Aboriginal & Torres Strait Islander Support</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Yagila Wadamba Exam Support Program</div>
      <p>Dedicated exam preparation support for Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander doctors.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
